-- Jordan Asks IMF for $2 Billion Loan, Al Arab Al Yawm Reports
-- B y   M o h a m m a d   T a y s e e r
-- 2012-05-22T13:45:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-22/jordan-asks-imf-for-2-billion-loan-al-arab-al-yawm-reports.html
Jordan  has asked the International
Monetary Fund for a $2 billion loan, the Al Arab Al Yawm
newspaper reported, citing an unidentified official.  The IMF is asking Jordan to lift subsidies on some products
and services and impose new taxes, it reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
